Duties and Responsibilities:
1.制定测试计划、设计测试方案、编写测试用例、执行测试、记录和跟踪 BUG，并分析给出测试报告;Draw up test plan, design test cases and implement tests, record and track BUGs, analyze and report
2.及时反映产品验收中的问题，对测试遗漏问题进行分析、能就现有系统提出质疑，发现问题及时与开发人员解决；
Timely report the problems found during the quality check; analyze the problem and find the solution with developers.
3.网站管理与内容管理。根据客户提供的文案或图片，将相应的内容放置于网站。包含文案检查，图片修改，样式排版调整；
Website and web content management; put content, words and pictures in the right place. check words, adjust pictures and optimize the layout;
4.微信公众号注册以及认证;
Wechat official account registration and verification;
5.网站备案以及公安备案;
ICP registration and police registration；
6.适应多任务的环境下，高效率和高质量的交付;
Can take multi-task at the same time, detail-oriented, high efficiency and high quality;
7.上级交办的其它事物；
Other related work assigned by superiors;

Knowledge, Skills and Abilities：
1.熟悉 Android , iOS , Windows，Mac OS 操作系统；
Familiar with Android, iOS, windows, Mac OS operating system;
2.熟悉测试基础理论、常用测试技术方法，有较高的质量意识；
Familiar with the basic theory of testing and testing methods with high quality senses;
3.熟练掌握缺陷跟踪工具，测试管理工具;
Familiar with defect tracking tools, test management tools etc.
4.思路清晰，积极主动, 细致耐心, 良好的沟通协作意识及团队合作精神
Clear thinking, highly proactive, detail-oriented, good communication skill with team spirit;

Qualifications, Training and Experience:
1.大专及以上学历;
College education or above;
2.1年以上小程序、H5、APP以及网站测试经验, 能够使用自动测试框架以及脚本;
At least 1year test experience in mini programs, H5,APP and websites; With the ability to use the automated test framework and scripts;
3. 做过测试、QA者优先；
With test experience or QA experience is a plus;

